text.en_US: ...A Trial it is you seek, and a trial you shall receive...
text.pt_BR: ...Um teste voc procura, e um teste voc receber...
text.ja_JP: ...これはお前が探し求め、そして受けるべき試練...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.ko_KR: ...당신이 원하는 건 시험, 그러면 시험을 받을 것입니다...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Du willst dich also prüfen lassen, so wollen wir dich prüfen...

text.en_US: ...Perception is a skill few can master...
text.pt_BR: ...Percepo  uma habilidade que poucos podem dominar...
text.ja_JP: ...知覚する力を使いこなすものは少ない...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.ko_KR: ...인지라는 기술을 숙달할 수 있는 건 오직 소수뿐입니다...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Wahrnehmung ist eine Fähigkeit, die nur wenige beherrschen...

text.en_US: ...This trial will test your awareness and wit...
text.pt_BR: ...Este desafio testar sua conscincia e inteligncia...
text.ja_JP: ...この試練はお前の知覚と機知を試すものだ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.ko_KR: ...이 시험은 당신의 자각과 기지를 시험할 것입니다...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.zh_CN: ...此试炼将测试你的感知和智慧...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Diese Prüfung testet deine Achtsamkeit und Scharfsinnigkeit...
text.zh_TW: ...此試煉將測試你的感知和智慧...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]

text.en_US: ...Catch the golden bug in the thicket \c[3]6 times\c[0]...
text.pt_BR: ...Capture o inseto dourado na mata \c[3]6 vezes\c[0]...
text.ja_JP: ...竹やぶの中に隠れた黄金の虫を\c[3]6回\c[0]捕まえてみろ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Fange den Goldenen Käfer im Dickicht \c[3]sechs Mal\c[0]...

text.en_US: ...But do so quickly, or else the trial is failed...
text.pt_BR: ...Mas faa isso rapidamente, ou ento o teste ser malsucedido...
text.ja_JP: ...だが急ぐことだ。さもなくば試練は失敗となる...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
text.zh_CN: ...但动作要快，否则试炼将会失败...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
text.de_DE: ... Doch tue es geschwind, oder du wirst scheitern...
text.zh_TW: ...但動作要快，否則試煉將會失敗...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]

text.en_US: ...Speak to me again if you wish to begin the trial...
text.pt_BR: ...Fale comigo novamente se voc deseja comear o teste...
text.ja_JP: ...試練を始めたければ、もう一度私に話しかけろ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.zh_CN: ...如果你想要开始试炼，就跟我说...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Sprich erneut mit mir, wenn du die Prüfung zu beginnen wünschst...
text.zh_TW: ...如果你想要開始試煉，就跟我說...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]

text.ja_JP: ...やめたいときも、私に話しかけろ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.zh_CN: ...如果你想退出，也可以来找我...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Oder abzubrechen...
text.zh_TW: ...如果你想退出，也可以來找我...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]

message.en_US: Nooooooooo...\. Don't make me chase the bug.\. Not inside the bamboo maze.\. It could hide ANYWHERE!
message.pt_BR: Naaaaoooo...\. No me obrigue a perseguir esse inseto.\. No dentro do labirinto de bambu.\. Ele pode se esconder em QUALQUER LUGAR!
message.zh_CN: 不.....\.别让我抓虫子啊。\.还是在竹林迷宫里。\.这玩意儿可能躲在任何地方！<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.ja_JP:
いやああぁぁぁ...\.
虫を追いかけるなんてやだよ。\.
それもこんな竹やぶの迷路の中で。\.
どこに潜んでるかわからないじゃない！<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.ko_KR: 안 돼애애애애...\. 난 벌레를 쫓아가고 싶지 않아.\. 그것도 대나무 미로 안에서.\. 어디에 숨을지 모른다고!<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/08]
message.de_DE: Neiiiiiiiin...\. Zwingt mich nicht, den Käfer zu jagen.\. Nicht in einem Bambuslabyrinth.\. Der könnte sich ja ÜBERALL verstecken!
message.zh_TW: 不.....\.別讓我抓蟲子啊。\.還是在竹林迷宮裡。\.這東西可能躲在任何地方！<<A<<[CHANGED 2020/07/09]

text.de_DE: ... Du bist zurück...

text.en_US: ...Do you wish to begin your trial...
text.ja_JP: ...試練を始めたいというのだな...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/09/19]
text.de_DE: ... Wünschst du, die Prüfung zu beginnen?...
... Wie du wünschst...
... Wie du wünschst...
... Bist du bereit?...

text.en_US: ...Take your position next to the bug...
text.pt_BR: ... Se posicione ao lado do inseto....
text.ja_JP: ...では、虫の隣に並べ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Stell dich neben dem Käfer auf deine Position...
... Möge die Prüfung beginnen...

text.en_US: ...Take this token as a sign of your victory...

text.ja_JP: ...これをお前の勝利の証として受け取るがいい...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Nimm dies als Zeichen unserer Anerkennung...

text.ja_JP: ...油断しないことだ、探索者よ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2021/05/22]

text.ja_JP: ...時間切れだ、探索者よ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Die Zeit ist um, Seeker...

text.en_US: ...You didn't even find the bug once...
text.pt_BR: ...Voc nem sequer encontrou o inseto uma nica vez...

text.en_US: ...There is still much you need to learn...
text.ja_JP: ...お前にはまだ学ぶべきことがある...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]
text.de_DE: ... Du hast noch viel zu lernen, Seeker...

text.ja_JP: ...試練に再び挑みたくば話しかけるがいい...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]

text.ja_JP: ...よくやった、探索者よ...<<A<<[CHANGED 2018/05/01]

text.en_US: ...Come to me to claim your reward...
